<h2 id="lessons" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2 mt-4">Key Takeaways</h2>
<ol class="list-decimal list-inside">
    <li><a href="#learned1" class="text-green-800 dark:text-green-200">Don't forget Audio!</a></li>
</ol>

<h2 id="goals" class="font-semibold text-xl mt-4 mb-2">Goals</h2>
<p>We wanted our game audio to:</p>
<ul class="list-disc ml-8">
    <li>Capture the feeling of going on a grand adventure</li>
    <li>Create an uplifting, active atmosphere</li>
    <li>Avoid being jarring or distracting from gameplay</li>
</ul>
<p class="mt-2">We initially planned to have four audio tracks for the game:</p>
<ul class="list-disc ml-8">
    <li>The Great Hall</li>
    <li>The Cellar</li>
    <li>Boss Encounter</li>
    <li>Main Theme</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="inspiration" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2 mt-4">Inspirations</h2>
<p>We had a few key inspirations for audio. Our audio was mainly inspired by Stardew Valley, Lil Gator Game, and Celeste.</p>
<p class="mt-2">We used the following songs from these games as inspiration for each track:</p>
<ul class="list-disc ml-8">
    <li>
        The Great Hall
        <ul class="list-disc ml-8">
            <li>
                <p><a class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-300" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UKVuj7ygOHQ&list=PLzDYU_yTyBvLXyduKS61L0JOMTUhfGvPt&index=17" target="_blank">Creak Winds</a> - Lil Gator Game Creek</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
        The Cellar and Boss Encounter
        <ul class="list-disc ml-8">
            <li>
                <p><a class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-300" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JecdkxSZob8" target="_blank">Marimba of Frozen Bones</a> - Stardew Valley</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p><a class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-300" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YjgOzSQNQ0" target="_blank">Resurrections</a> - Celeste</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p><a class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-300" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xr9wHI51Zao&list=PLzDYU_yTyBvLXyduKS61L0JOMTUhfGvPt&index=24" target="_blank">Forest Winds</a> - Lil Gator Game</p>
