{# LESSON 1 #}
<div class="mb-8 rounded-lg p-2 mt-8 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg">
    <h3 id="learned1" class="font-semibold">Lesson 1: Don't forget Audio!</h3>
    <p class="ml-8">From other projects, we know audio is often neglected until the later stages of production, which can lead to underdeveloped products and a lack of player feedback. We wanted to address audio early by finding and implementing placeholder sounds before finding final assets, which worked well for us.</p>
</div>

